Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:22.12,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuha, Shino. It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:24.80,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.80,0:00:26.50,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:48.14,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like all of you are getting really good at preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.14,0:00:51.42,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,It's a huge help for such a busy period.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:54.74,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:58.95,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,You should all go for something sweet occasionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.88,0:01:02.82,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:05.83,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Mai, it's "much appreciated" when expressing gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:09.84,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:15.22,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, you have to give your best today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:17.84,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:31.11,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuha-san and Shino-san always seem so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.31,0:01:33.86,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:36.74,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:44.46,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Ouch....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:48.81,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Have you not gotten used to the boxed pillow, Midori-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.17,0:02:50.75,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:53.07,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,You seem to be doing well, Riko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.07,0:02:55.84,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I am largely used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:57.42,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Mai, you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:03:01.23,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but my neck still hurts a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:03.60,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,But lying on top of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:06.96,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,gives me a sense of really being an actual Maiko. I'm pretty happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:10.75,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I just hope this apprentice period can be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.92,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,There is no helping that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:19.34,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Now, let's start breakfast preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:20.10,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:21.25,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:28.85,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Making breakfast for the land lady and the other sisters at Kikuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:31.34,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,That's our responsibility as apprentices.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:37.58,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Riko-chan, Kamado (stove) is called Okudosan in Kyoto, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:40.24,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, you really know quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:43.90,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder when will we be able to use the stove?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:45.49,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Seems like it'd be delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:46.74,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:50.49,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Have you decided on what go with Miso soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:52.25,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Let's decide together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:53.75,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:55.70,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Wakame and Aburaage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:58.91,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,We've been going with that recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:03.09,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Mai-san remarked that it was delicious the other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:05.01,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go with that today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:08.08,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I'll handle the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:10.16,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I will do the sweeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:22.42,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,It's not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:24.78,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:37.08,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,What are you grinning at me, Mai-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:41.84,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Well, no.... Do you want another bowl of rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:53.02,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Dance recital?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:57.31,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Correct. Invitation from the tourism board.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:05:01.03,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Asked if we could assist them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:05.03,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Good. I think it would be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:13.64,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,The few of you are going be to taking lessons from Miyagawa on Ondo starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:19.52,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,You will have to dance on the Maiko test. The three of you have to buck up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:22.67,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:42.82,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:45.44,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,You three are always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:51.20,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,All the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:06:04.02,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Our teacher was said to be a famous Maiko known as the "period flower" back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:07.21,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,We are in your care for today, teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:09.22,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,We are in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:14.58,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Shall we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:18.23,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Whoever dances well today gets a Hanamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.26,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,We will try our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:24.36,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,We privately call her as the Hanamaru teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:36.75,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Riko, you danced well. Have a Hanamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:39.69,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,It is much appreciated, teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:43.51,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Midori, you have to be softer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:46.40,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Your stance now is stiff like Karate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:49.26,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Much appreciated, Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:52.76,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Mai, it is good you grasp it fast,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:55.51,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,but you have to put more heart into your dance next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:07:01.25,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,It's... much appreciated, Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:07.49,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, wanna drop by somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:08.75,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Down by?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:12.45,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Midori-san, do you have somewhere in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:14.45,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.38,0:07:16.95,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Cafe!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:20.46,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Onee-san gave us some allowance a few days ago, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:22.46,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Let's have cake with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:38.06,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,What a long queue!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:42.29,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's best we give up for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:46.94,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Hanami-koji is a really popular tourist attraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:48.55,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Let's come next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:49.85,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I crave for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.85,0:07:54.64,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, I've been here before during my school excursion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:03.12,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Kyoto was at its rainy season.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.26,0:08:11.21,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing alone somewhere like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:21.23,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Are you a student from the excursion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:31.04,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Let me do it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:37.51,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,If Kazuha-san did not tell to me that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:40.24,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,the thought of being a Maiko never would have crossed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:47.00,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,More importantly, I can never forget those words she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:50.50,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I am a Maiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:56.84,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I feel this is a job rich in heritage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:04.10,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,In addition, this is a job that most represents Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:13.40,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Um, could you take a picture for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:16.91,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:19.41,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:21.00,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,1 + 1 = ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:22.67,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:25.54,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:26.46,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.17,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Are you on a field trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:31.01,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, are you from Kyoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.01,0:09:33.96,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Well... I guess you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:37.30,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,We are students learning the art of Maiko. Everyone of us is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:39.40,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Is that true!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:42.31,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, they are Maikos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:45.81,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Maiko!? Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:51.84,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,It's kind of embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:53.02,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:57.21,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,A year ago, I was the one asking for to take photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:10:01.68,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,But Mai-san and Midori-san are already Kyotolites.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:02.27,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:03.73,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:04.95,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:08.91,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, shall we look for the granny at the draper's store?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:11.45,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:12.71,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:15.28,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,The draper's granny we are referring to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:18.41,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,is the owner of Itami; a draper store in the district.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:21.60,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,She is an old friend of Kikuya's land lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:25.85,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,You came at the right time. Try some of the snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:27.41,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Right on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:28.94,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:30.60,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,It is very much appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:34.11,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,That is correct. You should use "much appreciated".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:42.66,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,It's not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:44.22,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,It's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.22,0:10:45.24,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:50.25,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Our Kimono and cakes are the best in business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.01,0:10:56.05,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,That is really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:59.78,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right? I especially like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:01.26,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:04.69,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,It's gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:07.80,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,You really love Kimonos, don't you? Mai-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:11.29,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, for some reason, I've liked them since I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:13.99,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,When you become a full fledged Maiko,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:16.02,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,i'll send you a Kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:17.48,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:20.60,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,You should ask your father, Midori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:24.68,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Your family is so rich, they will surely get you piles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:27.40,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to depend on my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:29.29,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Well, what a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:33.80,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,But this is what I admire Midori-san for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:35.80,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Then I'll have the cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:37.98,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,That was mine....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.98,0:11:39.74,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you admired me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:46.08,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,What have you written today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:48.30,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,About how we met the field trip students.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:50.46,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:52.02,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Do you want to write too, Riko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.19,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I shall do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.55,0:11:55.89,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,The two of you love to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:12:00.25,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I can never bring myself to write diary or things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:04.52,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,We will write your share on your behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:08.06,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Right, this year's Gion Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:12.43,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,will feature a dance recital organized by the tourism association.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:19.59,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, this morning my mother seemed to have mentioned something like that to Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:23.87,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,It's a good chance for aspiring Maikos to take the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:31.98,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, the recital?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:36.69,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Mother have mentioned about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:38.76,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Saying we have to contribute to the programme.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:40.98,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,But apparently we are only sending two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:43.98,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Shino-chan, I failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:45.57,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:54.81,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Two people, which means only two of us get to perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:58.40,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,What should we do...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:02.13,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Which means Riko is definitely selected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:04.22,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,There's only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:06.76,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,It is not confirmed that I will be selected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:11.21,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,You will make it since you get the most Hanamarus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:15.29,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,What's left is whether Mai or me gets it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:20.17,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,But my mom has yet to formally speak to us about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:22.43,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Wanna go ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:26.15,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,But did the draper granny not mention?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:29.39,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Before the land lady brings up the topic,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:32.19,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,keep it a secret about me bringing up the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:36.04,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. I don't think it's appropriate for us to ask now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:42.22,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Well, regardless of who gets picked, no hard feelings and we'll all work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:43.27,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:44.63,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.36,0:14:13.49,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,You're up early, Midori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:16.57,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Normally, you won't wake up no matter how much I try.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:19.83,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,We are afterall going to be rivals from today on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:21.58,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:24.93,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Well.... how should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:26.99,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,We have to work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:31.22,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I'll feel bad for making you two look after me like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:33.72,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I'll head down first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:38.48,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Midori-san has this side of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:41.94,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we have to work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:42.98,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:46.74,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Wrong! Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:49.28,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,What's with you, Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.64,0:14:50.72,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:56.79,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Your shoulders have been less stiff lately and your movements have improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:58.85,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Now it's as stiff as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:00.59,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Your face looks scary, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:10.97,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm back to square one....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.80,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:14.36,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:19.54,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Both of you have it good today. Managing to get the Hanamarus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:23.35,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, I have to buck up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:27.82,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Midori-chan. Wanna drop by the draper's granny store along the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:32.32,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Ingredients for dinner have also been bought, so it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:37.49,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not going. Both of you should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:54.97,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Knowing Midori-chan, she's probably practicing on her own right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:57.17,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:15:59.53,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,It feels sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.53,0:16:04.23,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,One of us will not perform at the recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.35,0:16:20.06,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,That's not right.... Gentler.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:22.16,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Midori-chan, wanna take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:24.38,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,We have cake for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:28.27,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I'll skip for now. I've to practice or I won't be able to catch up with you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:40.47,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Midori-chan is still practicing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:43.27,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:48.73,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,What will happen if these feelings persist until the recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:54.24,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,If only the three of us can perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:16:59.74,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:02.10,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:23.27,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Let's decide what goes with goes with Miso soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:24.02,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:26.69,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,There's no need. Just go with what you what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:29.12,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,No, let's all decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:31.90,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,One, two! Wakame and Aburaage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:36.91,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:45.65,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Midori-san seems really sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:49.01,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like she practiced late into the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:51.80,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Is she not getting enough sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:54.93,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Before hearing about the recital,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:17:58.06,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,it's always the three of us, be it housework or lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:18:02.58,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Since we are all working hard, I'd prefer we do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:05.56,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I'll do the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:21.70,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Here, the Kimono I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:24.05,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Convey my greetings to the land lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.05,0:18:25.70,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:27.88,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:32.19,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm here alone today to run an errand for my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:36.34,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,But I'd still prefer the three of us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.53,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:38.84,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:44.08,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,It's strange. You're not like the usual Mai-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:47.64,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,You're right. It's gotten really strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:50.74,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I feel as if we have become distant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:06.60,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Unknowingly, the Gion Festival approaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:11.77,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,The Gion Festival is coming soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:14.71,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:17.96,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,What about the recital?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:23.97,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Are we really performing? Mom hasn't told us anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:31.95,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I'll ask granny about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:36.12,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's more natural for you as her niece to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:36.90,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:55.54,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,If you'd please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:57.37,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Much appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:01.30,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:04.05,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,During work, call me Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:06.21,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:12.44,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Mother, it's regarding the dance recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:15.05,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:16.43,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:20.23,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's going to be a first job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.23,0:20:22.55,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,It's natural to wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:25.04,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I guess it's time to make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:32.69,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,There's really a recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:38.81,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Which means that very soon, one of us is going to be left out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:41.34,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,That's surely me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:43.13,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,You never know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:44.59,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,It's yet to be decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:47.62,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. No need to console me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:54.91,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,My dance is inferior compared to you two. I know that very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:01.21,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Midori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.43,0:21:06.11,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I don't wish for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:09.70,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,If I knew this would happen, I wouldn't perform at the recital or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:14.76,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about! This is a chance to perform!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:19.41,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Passing up the opportunity for me. You can't say something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:33.60,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,It's been two months at Kikuya for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:35.85,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Maiko training is tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:39.59,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,But as I have friends working hard together, I was about to carry on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.25,0:21:43.78,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Because Midori-chan and Riko-chan are with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:51.63,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, why is it that only two of us can attend?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.36,0:21:59.25,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,I'll ask mother why can't the three of us perform together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:00.86,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:01.92,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Mai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:09.54,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.54,0:22:12.18,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong. You look conflicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.63,0:22:16.56,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,It's regarding the dance recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.56,0:22:19.57,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Why restrict it to two persons?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.57,0:22:21.49,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Can't it be the three of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.47,0:22:31.07,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.02,0:22:35.36,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it's the dance recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.36,0:22:39.58,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,We heard only two of us would be chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.58,0:22:42.48,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Are you perhaps mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.48,0:22:44.88,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,The recital is for all Okiyas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:46.84,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Of course everybody has to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.23,0:22:49.32,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,But Kazuha-san said
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.32,0:22:51.23,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,only two of us may go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.23,0:22:52.85,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,She said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:22:57.35,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Wrong. The restriction is for two performances.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:22:58.85,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,EH!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:03.48,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,But when you said it's about time to decide....
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.48,0:23:05.87,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,It means to ensure we don't clash with programs of the other Okiyas,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.87,0:23:09.86,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,we have to decide soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:12.54,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,So that's what it meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.54,0:23:14.53,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Which means we....
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:17.00,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,can perform together?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:19.00,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.81,0:23:22.11,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.11,0:23:24.00,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:26.50,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.95,0:23:28.21,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.45,0:23:30.81,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.28,0:23:54.28,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Did I say only two of you can perform?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.28,0:23:55.32,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.32,0:23:56.28,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.28,0:24:00.29,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,The manner of speech might differ, but we clearly heard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.29,0:24:02.85,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Oh dear. I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.85,0:24:04.68,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,But isn't that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.68,0:24:07.69,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,The three of you having your maiden performance together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.69,0:24:10.47,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,We didn't have such good fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.47,0:24:13.77,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. How envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.77,0:24:15.92,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Well, give it your best shot, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.51,0:24:19.41,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,That's how it is....
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.41,0:24:21.81,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuha-san is quite a handful....
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.26,0:24:25.86,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,But it's wonderful that we be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.86,0:24:26.81,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.81,0:24:29.78,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Then we should also decide that today.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.78,0:24:30.94,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.94,0:24:32.09,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.09,0:24:33.07,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.07,0:24:35.03,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Wakame and tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.03,0:24:38.04,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Oh! Fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.04,0:24:40.15,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,We got tofu right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.15,0:24:42.54,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,And aburaage is what we usually go for.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.90,0:24:46.54,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,The three of them are really closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.21,0:24:48.63,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.48,0:25:23.33,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,You three look gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.33,0:25:24.96,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Give it your best shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.92,0:25:27.27,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.79,0:27:36.99,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,It was really fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.99,0:27:38.26,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.40,0:27:42.76,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Let's make sure the three of us become Maikos.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.76,0:27:43.56,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.56,0:27:44.39,Mitsuwano_Main,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.81,0:25:50.06,Alt OP English,,0,0,0,,You called out to me when it is pouring
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.33,0:25:59.41,Alt OP English,,0,0,0,,Time started moving from that moment on
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.42,0:26:03.54,Alt OP English,,0,0,0,,Words that are hard to honestly say
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.54,0:26:07.21,Alt OP English,,0,0,0,,Stuff that we cannot seem to do well
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.21,0:26:16.59,Alt OP English,,0,0,0,,We may be frustrated whenever we reach a hurdle
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.59,0:26:22.60,Alt OP English,,0,0,0,,But we have to keep embracing those never changing feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.81,0:26:27.28,Alt OP English,,0,0,0,,Even when we feel useless and lost
